  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Implementing the UN Guiding Principles on Business and Human Rights in the Colombian mining sector</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project promotes knowledge of the human rights impacts of mining gold and construction materials and develops tools for their prevention, mitigation and access to non judicial remedies with the government, mining companies, community based organisations and civil society organisations. The project supports an evidence based strategy and policy document on access and use of non judicial remedy to human rights grievances delivered to the Colombian government.</narrative>
